@node 1 "What the fuck..."

SnatchDIZ  is  another  FILE_ID.DIZ extractor for the Shell or for use with
any bbs-system.  Features:

 - LHA-, LZX-, ZIP-, RAR-, XPK-, DMS-, EXE-, GIF-, TXT-support
 - /X style listfile generation
 - file_id.diz -> filecomment conversion
 - SnatchDIZ is very small and faaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaast (1oo% assembly)!
 - great code: SnatchDIZ does not produce HITS like WhaDIZ, SpeeDIZ etc.
 - reentrant (can be made resident)
 - good error handling: no problems with empty files or something

-=> Use SnatchDIZ instead of all the other crap floating around!
@endnode
@node 2 "It's easy..."

Usage: SnatchDIZ FILE/A,S=SUPPRESS/S,LF=LISTFILE/K,D2C=DIZ2COMMENT/S
====================================================================

@{b}example 1:@{ub}  "SnatchDIZ dh0:down/PPLAY41.LZX S" will give you

--------------------------------------
Power Player 4.1 Final Omega Version
* Latest Update! *
--------------------------------------

This extracts and shows the file_id.diz and suppresses the credits and the
filetype indicator.


@{b}example 2:@{ub}  "SnatchDIZ dh0:down/!s-w&f.lha S LF ram:listfile" will show you
the  file_id.diz  and add it to the listfile ram:listfile.  If ram:listfile
does not exist it will be created.

The listfile looks like this:

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
!s-w&f.lha               37137     __/\____/\____/\____:_/\___/\____/\___/\__ 
                                   \  ___\_ _____ ___/ |  /___ ___\  ____  __\ 
                                  _/\_ \ /  |_/  __)/  l_ \/  __)_/\_ \ |  |\/ 
                                  \     \   ` \  l  \      \  l  \     \|  |lr
                                  /_____/____ /_____/__/\__/_____/_____/l__!d 
                                  ======[ sCENESt pARTY cONTRiBUTiON ]========
                                  -                                          -
                                  -       wATER & fIRE - first place         -
                                  -                                          -
                                  -     a small *40kb* intro by tHERAPY      -
                                  ==============================[09/04/95]====
------------------------------------------------------------------------------


@{b}example 3:@{ub} "SnatchDIZ dh0:down/hf-bl060.lha D2C"

will show you the file_id.diz and convert it into the filecomment.


@{b}HINT:@{ub} SnatchDIZ does NOT directly support wildcards! However you can
      easily use the script "SPat" which should be in your S: to do that.
      Look into the script "GenListFile" how that works.


@{b}WARNING: - SnatchDIZ is cli-only so don't start from Workbench!@{ub}
@endnode
@node 3 "You got this crap..."

You need:

 - an AMIGA w/Kick 2.04+ (as always).
 - the lha-, lzx-, UNzip- and UNrar-executable placed in your path.
   A working UNzip and UNrar is included in the SnatchDIZ-archive.

That's it.
@endnode
